00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.860
Pancake Recipe - How to make crepes
&gt;&gt;Pancake recipe classic crepes

00:00:00.860 --> 00:00:05.800
This tutorial will show you step by step how
to make crepes, a popular pancake recipe that's

00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:10.059
simple to make
To make 4, you will need

00:00:10.059 --> 00:00:17.390
4oz or 115g of all purpose flour
1/4 tablespoon of salt

00:00:17.390 --> 00:00:23.870
1 egg
10 fl oz or 300ml of milk

00:00:23.870 --> 00:00:32.480
A alittle unsalted butter fro frying
Lemon wedges and sugar to serve

00:00:32.480 --> 00:00:36.339
A frying pan
A pallatte knife

00:00:36.339 --> 00:00:39.529
If you want to make more than 4 just double
the ingredients

00:00:39.529 --> 00:00:46.029
Step 1
From a height, sift the flour and salt into

00:00:46.029 --> 00:00:51.939
a large bowl and make a well in the center
Crack the egg into the well along with half

00:00:51.939 --> 00:00:57.980
the milk and wisk together gradually drawing
in flour from the sides to make a smooth,

00:00:57.980 --> 00:01:02.850
thin batter
Gradually add the remaining milk beating until

00:01:02.850 --> 00:01:09.960
smooth
Leave to stand for 10 minutes

00:01:09.960 --> 00:01:14.800
Step 2
Preheat the oven to its lowest setting.

00:01:14.800 --> 00:01:19.899
Place the drying pan on the stove on a medium-high
heat and add a knob of butter, making sure

00:01:19.899 --> 00:01:24.550
it coats the pan
Ladle about three tablespoons of batter into

00:01:24.550 --> 00:01:29.939
the center of the pan and tilt so that it
covers the base thinly

00:01:29.939 --> 00:01:35.890
Cook for 1 to 2 minutes, or until bubbles
appear, then slide a palette knife underneath

00:01:35.890 --> 00:01:40.759
and flip over.
Continue cooking for 30 seconds or until golden

00:01:40.759 --> 00:01:47.330
Step 3
Remove, transfer to a plate and keep warm

00:01:47.330 --> 00:01:52.060
in the oven.
Repeat this process until the batter has been

00:01:52.060 --> 00:01:56.429
used up.
Step 4

00:01:56.429 --> 00:02:01.979
Serve your pancakes hot, sprinkled with sugar
and lemon juice

00:02:01.979 --> 00:02:06.889
If you want to dry other flavors a drizzle
of maple syrup, chocolate sauce or pieces

00:02:06.889 --> 00:02:08.910
or fresh fruit will taste great with these
pancakes

